-- Yu Yongding Says China Can't Avoid, Mustn't Fear Exchange-Rate Adjustment
-- B y   S h a m i m   A d a m   a n d   D a v i d   Y o n g
-- 2010-09-28T10:17:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-28/yu-yongding-says-china-can-t-avoid-mustn-t-fear-exchange-rate-adjustment.html
China cannot avoid an adjustment in
its exchange rate, either real or nominal, and should not be
afraid of such changes, Yu Yongding, a former adviser to the
central bank, said in a speech in Singapore today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Yong in Singapore at 
